{
  "stem": "2980.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I believe it was in 1928.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The United States government.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Poland still was willing to let him out, but the US government denied.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went instead to Argentina, as a-- as a farmer, as a farm worker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was somewheres in 1928.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My immediate family, my mother was trying to get papers from the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they tried to make papers out for us to come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were already a family of five, six.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in school in 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember instead of having classes, the teacher said all children must go out into the hallway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big hallway, and they had one radio.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the corner of the room was hanging, a wooden radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we must listen to that special announcement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we said it was kind of strange.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew from the parents that things are happening in the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we heard that in Germany things are happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were throwing out Jews and shooting and killing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was only 1939, I believe it was September first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that point, they started announcing that the German is demanding a part of Poland, and Poland wouldn't give in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And their big hero [INAUDIBLE] said no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And because of that, the Germans marched into Poland and the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The war broke out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it happened that in one day he ran away from Poland and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in 14 days the Germans crossed all of Poland, and 14 days after they were in our town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning they marched in, and they opened up soup kitchens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would give the soup to the tens of thousands of refugees who had-- who had run form west to east, towards Russia.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
